  <div class="c-entry-hero__content l-segment l-feature">
    
    
    <h1 class="c-page-title">How to tax the rich, explained</h1>

    <p class="c-entry-summary p-dek">It’s no accident that the Democratic Party went from wanting a 39.6 percent top tax rate to wanting much more.</p>

    <div class="c-byline">
  <span class="c-byline-wrapper">
    
      
        By
        <span class="c-byline__item">
          
            
